        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Thriving Community Gardens Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows local educational agencies to use Student Support and Academic Enrichment grants for the development and maintenance of school or community gardens. Additionally, the bill directs the Department of Education to regularly collect information and publish best practices for the development and maintenance of community gardens.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
